<h1 id="getting-started">Getting started</h1>

<p>In beamer terminology, a â€˜frameâ€™ is defined as a slide. Each frame in org-beamer-mode
can be specified using a heading (starting with <code>*</code> or <code>**</code> depending on the indentation
level that you have set).</p>

